{
  "spec": "# Component Specification: Dashboard\n\n**Page:** Dashboard (Main)\n**Project:** AgentForge\n**Spec Version:** 1.0\n**WCAG Target:** AA Compliance\n\n---\n\n## 1. Component Tree\n\n```\nDashboard (Page Root)\n├── TopNavigationBar\n│   ├── NavBrand (Logo + Home anchor)\n│   ├── NavLinkGroup\n│   │   ├── NavLink (x N)\n│   └── NavActions\n│       └── NotificationBell\n│           └── UnreadBadge\n│\n├── NotificationsDrawer (overlay, conditionally rendered)\n│   ├── DrawerBackdrop\n│   ├── DrawerPanel\n│   │   ├── DrawerHeader\n│   │   │   ├── DrawerTitle\n│   │   │   └── DrawerCloseButton\n│   │   ├── DrawerToolbar\n│   │   │   ├── MarkAllReadButton\n│   │   │   └── ViewAllLink\n│   │   └── NotificationFeed\n│   │       └── NotificationItem (x N)\n│   │           ├── NotificationIcon\n│   │           ├── NotificationContent\n│   │           │   ├── NotificationMessage\n│   │           │   └── NotificationTimestamp\n│   │           └── UnreadIndicatorDot\n│\n├── DashboardPageLayout\n│   ├── PageHeader\n│   │   ├── GreetingLabel\n│   │   └── LastRefreshedTimestamp\n│   │\n│   ├── KeyMetricsStrip\n│   │   ├── MetricCard [Total Active Tasks]\n│   │   │   ├── MetricValue\n│   │   │   └── MetricLabel\n│   │   ├── MetricCard [Tasks Completed]\n│   │   │   ├── MetricValue\n│   │   │   └── MetricLabel\n│   │   ├── MetricCard [Overdue Count]\n│   │   │   ├── MetricValue (urgent variant)\n│   │   │   ├── MetricLabel\n│   │   │   └── UrgencyIcon\n│   │   └── MetricCard [At-Risk Items]\n│   │       ├── MetricValue (urgent variant)\n│   │       ├── MetricLabel\n│   │       └── UrgencyIcon\n│   │\n│   ├── ContentGrid\n│   │   ├── ActiveTasksSummaryPanel\n│   │   │   ├── SectionHeader\n│   │   │   │   ├── SectionTitle (h2)\n│   │   │   │   └── ViewAllLink\n│   │   │   ├── StatusBreakdownBar\n│   │   │   │   ├── StatusSegment [In Progress]\n│   │   │   │   ├── StatusSegment [Blocked]\n│   │   │   │   └── StatusSegment [In Review]\n│   │   │   ├── PriorityDistributionGroup\n│   │   │   │   └── PriorityCountChip (x N)\n│   │   │   └── QuickActionEntry\n│   │   │       └── CreateTaskButton\n│   │   │\n│   │   └── TeamWorkloadPanel\n│   │       ├── SectionHeader\n│   │       │   ├── SectionTitle (h2)\n│   │       │   └── ViewAllLink\n│   │       ├── WorkloadList\n│   │       │   └── WorkloadMemberRow (x N)\n│   │       │       ├── MemberAvatar\n│   │       │       ├── MemberName\n│   │       │       ├── CapacityBar\n│   │       │       │   ├── CapacityFill\n│   │       │       │   └── OverloadIndicator (conditional)\n│   │       │       └── AssignmentCount\n│   │       └── WorkloadEmptyState (conditional)\n│   │           ├── EmptyIllustration\n│   │           ├── EmptyMessage\n│   │           └── EmptyCTA\n│\n└── SkeletonOverlay (conditional, loading state)\n    ├── MetricCardSkeleton (x 4)\n    ├── TasksPanelSkeleton\n    └── WorkloadPanelSkeleton\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. Component Specifications\n\n### 2.1 TopNavigationBar\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<header>` / `<nav>` |\n| **Position** | `position: sticky; top: 0` |\n| **Min height** | `64px` |\n| **Z-index** | `z-index: 1100` (token: `sticky`) |\n| **Background** | `surface-elevated` → `#FAFAF8` |\n| **Shadow** | `elevation level 1` → `0 2px 8px rgba(15,110,86,0.06)` |\n| **Layout** | Flexbox; `justify-content: space-between; align-items: center` |\n| **Padding** | `0 24px` (token spacing: `32` on wide) |\n\n#### NavBrand\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<a href=\"/\">` |\n| **Role** | Navigation landmark anchor |\n| **Min touch target** | `44×44px` |\n| **Focus ring** | `2px solid deep-teal (#0F6E56)`, `outline-offset: 2px` |\n\n#### NavLinkGroup\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<ul role=\"list\">` inside `<nav aria-label=\"Primary navigation\">` |\n| **Layout** | Flex row, `gap: 8px` |\n| **Mobile behavior** | Collapses to hamburger menu at `< 768px` |\n\n#### NotificationBell\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<button aria-label=\"Notifications\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\">` |\n| **Min touch target** | `44×44px` |\n| **Icon size** | `24×24px` |\n| **Focus ring** | `2px solid deep-teal`, `outline-offset: 2px` |\n| **Keyboard** | Activates drawer on `Enter` / `Space` |\n| **State** | `aria-expanded=\"true/false\"` reflecting drawer open state |\n\n#### UnreadBadge\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Position** | Absolute, top-right of bell icon |\n| **Background** | `error` → `coral-accent (#E8593C)` |\n| **Text color** | `text-on-cta` → `#FFF8E7` |\n| **Typography** | `label` scale — 12px, weight 500 |\n| **Display cap** | Max display: `\"99+\"` |\n| **Min size** | `18×18px`, `border-radius: pill (9999px)` |\n| **ARIA** | `aria-label=\"X unread notifications\"` on parent button |\n\n---\n\n### 2.2 NotificationsDrawer\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<div role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"drawer-title\">` |\n| **Z-index** | `1200` (token: `modal`) |\n| **Animation** | Slide in from right; `transform: translateX(0)`, `ease-out`, `200ms` |\n| **Reduced motion** | `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)` → opacity fade only, no translate |\n| **Width** | `360px` (desktop); `100vw` (mobile `< 640px`) |\n| **Height** | `100vh` |\n| **Background** | `surface-elevated` → `#FAFAF8` |\n| **Shadow** | `elevation level 3` → `0 8px 32px rgba(15,110,86,0.14)` |\n| **Focus trap** | Focus constrained within open drawer; returns to `NotificationBell` on close |\n| **Dismiss** | Close button (×), backdrop click, `Escape` key |\n\n#### DrawerBackdrop\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Background** | `overlay` → `rgba(0,0,0,0.5)` |\n| **Z-index** | `1199` (below drawer, above sticky nav) |\n| **Interaction** | Click closes drawer |\n\n#### DrawerCloseButton\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<button aria-label=\"Close notifications\">` |\n| **Min touch target** | `44×44px` |\n| **Focus ring** | `2px solid deep-teal`, `outline-offset: 2px` |\n\n#### NotificationItem\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Layout** | Flex row; icon + content + unread dot |\n| **Padding** | `16px` (token: `spacing[16]`) |\n| **Border-bottom** | `1px solid border-default (#9C9C97)` |\n| **Unread state** | Background `rgba(15,110,86,0.05)`; dot indicator `deep-teal` |\n| **Typography — message** | `body` → 14px, weight 400, `text-primary (#444441)` |\n| **Typography — timestamp** | `small` → 11px, weight 400, `text-secondary` *(see contrast note)* |\n\n#### MarkAllReadButton / ViewAllLink\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Min touch target** | `44px` height |\n| **Color** | `cta-primary` → `deep-teal (#0F6E56)` |\n| **Focus ring** | Standard token focus ring |\n\n---\n\n### 2.3 PageHeader\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Layout** | Flex row, `justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline` |\n| **Padding** | `32px 0 24px` |\n\n#### GreetingLabel\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<h1>` |\n| **Typography** | `heading-2` → 24px, weight 700, Nunito |\n| **Color** | `text-primary` → `#444441` |\n| **Example copy** | \"Good morning, Alex 👋\" |\n\n#### LastRefreshedTimestamp\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<p aria-live=\"polite\">` |\n| **Typography** | `label` → 12px, weight 500, Open Sans |\n| **Color** | `text-secondary` → `#9C9C97` *(audit required — see §5)* |\n| **Includes** | Manual refresh icon button (44×44px touch target) |\n\n---\n\n### 2.4 KeyMetricsStrip\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Layout** | CSS Grid, 4 columns desktop → 2 tablet → 1 mobile (see §4) |\n| **Gap** | `24px` (token: `spacing[24]`) |\n| **Role** | `<section aria-label=\"Key metrics\">` |\n\n#### MetricCard\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<article>` or `<div role=\"group\" aria-label=\"[Metric Name]: [Value]\">` |\n| **Background** | `surface-elevated` → `#FAFAF8` |\n| **Border-radius** | `medium` → `12px` |\n| **Shadow** | `elevation level 1` → `0 2px 8px rgba(15,110,86,0.06)` |\n| **Padding** | `24px` (token: `spacing[24]`) |\n| **Interactive** | Focusable; hover `0.08` opacity overlay; `cursor: pointer` |\n| **Focus ring** | `2px solid deep-teal`, `outline-offset: 2px` |\n| **Hover transition** | `100ms ease-out` (token: `fast`) |\n\n##### MetricValue\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Typography** | `heading-1` → 32px, weight 700, Nunito |\n| **Color (default)** | `text-primary` → `#444441` |\n| **Color (urgent: overdue/at-risk)** | `error` → `coral-accent (#E8593C)` |\n| **ARIA** | `aria-label` on card provides full context: `\"12 overdue tasks\"` |\n| **Live region** | `aria-live=\"polite\"` for auto-refresh updates |\n\n##### MetricLabel\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Typography** | `label` → 12px, weight 500, Open Sans |\n| **Color** | `text-secondary` → `#9C9C97` *(audit required)* |\n\n##### UrgencyIcon (overdue / at-risk cards only)\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Purpose** | Non-color redundancy for WCAG AA (color not sole indicator) |\n| **Color** | `coral-accent (#E8593C)` |\n| **Size** | `16×16px` |\n| **ARIA** | `aria-hidden=\"true\"` (label on card provides context) |\n\n---\n\n### 2.5 ActiveTasksSummaryPanel\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<section aria-labelledby=\"tasks-heading\">` |\n| **Background** | `surface-elevated` → `#FAFAF8` |\n| **Border-radius** | `medium` → `12px` |\n| **Shadow** | `elevation level 1` |\n| **Padding** | `24px` |\n\n#### SectionTitle\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<h2 id=\"tasks-heading\">` |\n| **Typography** | `heading-2` → 24px, weight 700, Nunito |\n| **Color** | `text-primary` → `#444441` |\n| **Example copy** | \"Active Tasks\" |\n\n#### StatusBreakdownBar\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Layout** | Horizontal segmented bar; flex row |\n| **Height** | `16px` |\n| **Border-radius** | `pill` on first/last segment ends |\n| **Role** | `role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Task status breakdown\"` |\n\n##### StatusSegment\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Interactive** | Clickable; navigates to filtered task list |\n| **Element** | `<button>` |\n| **Min touch target** | `44px` height (extend hit area via padding) |\n| **Hover** | `0.08` opacity overlay, `100ms ease-out` |\n| **Focus ring** | `2px solid deep-teal`, `outline-offset: 2px` |\n| **ARIA** | `aria-label=\"In Progress: 14 tasks\"` etc. |\n| **Colors** | In Progress: `deep-teal`; Blocked: `coral-accent`; In Review: muted `warm-gray-light` *(confirm with design)* |\n\n#### PriorityCountChip\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Layout** | Inline flex row of chips |\n| **Border-radius** | `small` → `8px` |\n| **Padding** | `4px 12px` |\n| **Typography** | `label` → 12px, weight 500 |\n| **Background** | Tinted per priority level *(priority color map TBD by design)* |\n\n#### CreateTaskButton\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Variant** | `cta-primary` |\n| **Background** | `deep-teal (#0F6E56)` |\n| **Text color** | `text-on-cta` → `#FFF8E7` |\n| **Border-radius** | `medium` → `12px` |\n| **Min touch target** | `44px` height |\n| **Typography** | `body` → 14px, weight 400 |\n| **Hover** | `0.08` opacity overlay on background, `100ms ease-out` |\n| **Focus ring** | `2px solid deep-teal`, `outline-offset: 2px` |\n\n---\n\n### 2.6 TeamWorkloadPanel\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<section aria-labelledby=\"workload-heading\">` |\n| **Background** | `surface-elevated` → `#FAFAF8` |\n| **Border-radius** | `medium` → `12px` |\n| **Shadow** | `elevation level 1` |\n| **Padding** | `24px` |\n\n#### SectionTitle\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<h2 id=\"workload-heading\">` |\n| **Typography** | `heading-2` → 24px, weight 700, Nunito |\n| **Example copy** | \"Your Team's Workload\" |\n\n#### WorkloadMemberRow\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | `<button>` or `<a>` (navigates to member detail) |\n| **Layout** | Flex row; avatar + name + capacity bar + count |\n| **Min touch target** | `44px` height |\n| **Hover** | `0.08` opacity overlay, `100ms ease-out` |\n| **Focus ring** | `2px solid deep-teal`, `outline-offset: 2px` |\n| **ARIA** | `aria-label=\"Jane Smith — 8 tasks assigned, overloaded\"` |\n\n##### MemberAvatar\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Size** | `32×32px` |\n| **Border-radius** | `pill` (circular) |\n| **Alt text** | Member name (if image); initials fallback |\n\n##### CapacityBar\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Role** | `role=\"progressbar\" aria-valuenow aria-valuemin=\"0\" aria-valuemax=\"100\"` |\n| **Height** | `8px` |\n| **Border-radius** | `pill` |\n| **Fill (healthy)** | `success` → `deep-teal (#0F6E56)` |\n| **Fill (overloaded)** | `error` → `coral-accent (#E8593C)` |\n| **Background track** | `rgba(68,68,65,0.12)` |\n\n##### OverloadIndicator\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Element** | Icon + label (non-color redundancy) |\n| **Color** | `coral-accent (#E8593C)` |\n| **ARIA** | `aria-hidden=\"true\"` (row label carries context) |\n\n#### WorkloadEmptyState\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Layout** | Centered flex column |\n| **Illustration** | Minimal line art, `deep-teal` + `coral-accent` accent colors |\n| **Message typography** | `heading-3` → 18px, weight 600, Nunito |\n| **CTA** | `CreateTaskButton` variant (or \"Add Team Member\") |\n| **ARIA** | `role=\"status\"` if dynamically inserted |\n\n---\n\n### 2.7 SkeletonOverlay\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| **Trigger** | Rendered during initial load and data refresh |\n| **Shape matching** | Skeletons match exact card/panel dimensions |\n| **Animation** | Shimmer pulse, `1.4s ease-in-out infinite`; suppressed under `prefers-reduced-motion` |\n| **Background** | `rgba(68,68,65,0.08)` shimmer on `surface-elevated` |\n| **ARIA** | `aria-busy=\"true\"` on parent section; `aria-label=\"Loading dashboard data\"` |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Layout Rules\n\n### 3.1 Page Shell\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  TopNavigationBar (sticky, z:1100, h:64px min)   │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  DashboardPageLayout                             │\n│  max-width: 1280px | margin: 0 auto              │\n│  padding: 0 24px                                 │\n│                                                  │\n│  PageHeader                                      │\n│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────  │\n│  KeyMetricsStrip [4-col grid]                    │\n│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────  │\n│  ContentGrid [2-col: tasks | workload]           │\n│                                                  │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 3.2 Grid System\n\n| Zone | Columns | Gutter | Behavior |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **KeyMetricsStrip** | 4 of 12 columns each | `24px` | Responsive reflow (see §4) |\n| **ContentGrid** | 7 col tasks / 5 col workload | `24px` | Stacks vertically below tablet |\n| **Page margin** | `24px` left/right | — | `32px` on wide (≥ 1440px) |\n\n### 3.3 Spacing Rhythm\n\n| Context | Token | Value |\n|---|---|---|\n| Between page sections | `spacing[48]` | `48px` |\n| Within panel padding | `spacing[24]` | `24px` |\n| Between metric cards | `spacing[24]` | `24px` |\n| Between workload rows | `spacing[12]` | `12px` |\n| Between nav items | `spacing[8]` | `8px` |\n| Drawer internal padding | `spacing[16]` | `16px` |\n\n### 3.4 Elevation Hierarchy\n\n| Layer | Level | Shadow |\n|---|---|---|\n| Page background | `0` | none |\n| Metric cards, panels | `1` | `0 2px 8px rgba(15,110,86,0.06)` |\n| Dropdowns, hover popovers | `2` | `0 4px 16px rgba(15,110,86,0.10)` |\n| Notifications drawer | `3` | `0 8px 32px rgba(15,110,86,0.14)` |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Responsive Breakpoints\n\n### 4.1 Breakpoint Definitions\n\n| Token | Value | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `mobile` | `< 640px` | Single-column, full-width |\n| `tablet` | `768px – 1023px` | 2-column metrics, stacked panels |\n| `desktop` | `1024px – 1279px` | Full multi-column layout |\n| `wide` | `≥ 1440px` | Max-width constrained, centered |\n\n### 4.2 Breakpoint Behavior Matrix\n\n| Component | Mobile `< 640px` | Tablet `768–1023px` | Desktop `1024–1279px` | Wide `≥ 1440px` |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| **TopNavigationBar** | Hamburger menu; bell icon remains visible | Hamburger or condensed links | Full nav links | Full nav links |\n| **KeyMetricsStrip** | 1 column stacked or horizontal scroll row | 2 × 2 grid | 4 × 1 row | 4 × 1 row |\n| **ContentGrid** | Single column; tasks above workload | Single column; tasks above workload | 2 columns (7/5 split) | 2 columns (7/5 split) |\n| **WorkloadMemberRow** | Compact card or accordion pattern | Compact list | Full row with capacity bar | Full row with capacity bar |\n| **NotificationsDrawer** | `width: 100vw` | `width: 360px` | `width: 360px` | `width: 360px` |\n| **Page padding** | `16px` horizontal | `24px` horizontal | `24px` horizontal | `32px` horizontal |\n| **Content max-width** | 100% | 100% | 1280px (centered) | 1280px (centered) |\n\n### 4.3 Mobile-Specific Rules\n\n- `KeyMetricsStrip`: If horizontal scroll row, include `scroll-snap-type: x mandatory` on container; each card `scroll-snap-align: start`; hide scrollbar visually but keep accessible.\n- Stacked panels use `margin-bottom: 24px` between each.\n- Touch targets expand to minimum `44×44px` — no exceptions.\n- Typography scale unchanged (do not reduce below spec sizes on mobile).\n\n---\n\n## 5. Token Bindings\n\n### 5.1 Color Token Bindings\n\n| Component / Element | Semantic Token | Primitive Value |\n|---|---|---|\n| Page background | `background-primary` | `#FFF8E7` |\n| TopNavigationBar background | `surface-elevated` | `#FAFAF8` |\n| Metric cards background | `surface-elevated` | `#FAFAF8` |\n| Section panels background | `surface-elevated` | `#FAFAF8` |\n| Primary headings (h1, h2) | `text-primary` | `#444441` |\n| Body text, messages | `text-primary` | `#444441` |\n| Secondary / supporting text | `text-secondary` ⚠️ | `#9C9C97` *(audit required)* |\n| Timestamps, labels | `text-secondary` ⚠️ | `#9C9C97` *(audit required)* |\n| CTA buttons (Create Task) | `cta-primary` | `#0F6E56` |\n| CTA button text | `text-on-cta` | `#FFF8E7` |\n| Overdue metric value | `error` | `#E8593C` |\n| At-risk metric value | `warning` | `#E8593C` |\n| Overloaded capacity fill | `error` | `#E8593C` |\n| Healthy capacity fill | `success` | `#0F6E56` |\n| UnreadBadge background | `error` | `#E8593C` |\n| UnreadBadge text | `text-on-cta` | `#FFF8E7` |\n| Focus rings (all interactive) | `border-focus` | `#0F6E56` |\n| Card borders (if used) | `border-default` | `#9C9C97` |\n| Error state borders | `border-error` | `#E8593C` |\n| Drawer backdrop | `overlay` | `rgba(0,0,0,0.5)` |\n| Status: In Progress | `success` | `#0F6E56` |\n| Status: Blocked | `error` | `#E8593C` |\n| Unread notification BG | `info` (tinted) | `rgba(15,110,86,0.05)` |\n\n> ⚠️ **Contrast Risk:** `text-secondary (#9C9C97)` on `background-primary (#FFF8E7)` must be audited before implementation. If failing 4.5:1 AA ratio, replace with `#767672` or restrict to bold/large text only.\n\n### 5.2 Typography Token Bindings\n\n| Component / Element | Role Token | Size | Weight | Family |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Page greeting (h1) | `heading-2` | 24px | 700 | Nunito |\n| Section titles (h2) | `heading-2` | 24px | 700 | Nunito |\n| Sub-section labels (h3) | `heading-3` | 18px | 600 | Nunito |\n| Metric values | `heading-1` | 32px | 700 | Nunito |\n| Metric labels | `label` | 12px | 500 | Open Sans |\n| Notification messages | `body` | 14px | 400 | Open Sans |\n| Notification timestamps | `small` | 11px | 400 | Open Sans |\n| Button labels | `body` | 14px | 400 | Open Sans |\n| UnreadBadge count | `label` | 12px | 500 | Open Sans |\n| Member names | `body` | 14px | 400 | Open Sans |\n| Assignment counts | `label` | 12px | 500 | Open Sans |\n| Last refreshed timestamp | `label` | 12px | 500 | Open Sans |\n\n### 5.3 Spacing Token Bindings\n\n| Usage | Token Index | Value |\n|---|---|---|\n| Page horizontal padding (desktop) | `spacing[24]` | `24px` |\n| Page horizontal padding (wide) | `spacing[32]` | `32px` |\n| Page horizontal padding (mobile) | `spacing[16]` | `16px` |\n| Between major sections | `spacing[48]` | `48px` |\n| Panel internal padding | `spacing[24]` | `24px` |\n| Metrics strip gap | `spacing[24]` | `24px` |\n| Workload row gap | `spacing[12]` | `12px` |\n| Drawer item padding | `spacing[16]` | `16px` |\n| Nav item gap | `spacing[8]` | `8px` |\n| Badge internal padding | `spacing[4]` vertical, `spacing[8]` horizontal | `4px / 8px` |\n\n### 5.4 Border & Shape Token Bindings\n\n| Element | Token | Value |\n|---|---|---|\n| Metric cards | `border-radius.medium` | `12px` |\n| Section panels | `border-radius.medium` | `12px` |\n| CTA buttons | `border-radius.medium` | `12px` |\n| Priority chips | `border-radius.small` | `8px` |\n| Avatar | `border-radius.pill` | `9999px` |\n| Unread badge | `border-radius.pill` | `9999px` |\n| Capacity bar | `border-radius.pill` | `9999px` |\n| Status bar segment ends | `border-radius.pill` | `9999px` |\n\n### 5.5 Motion Token Bindings\n\n| Interaction | Duration Token | Easing | Reduced Motion |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Notification drawer open/close | `normal` → `200ms` | `ease-out` | Opacity only, no translate |\n| Hover state feedback | `fast` → `100ms` | `ease-out` | No change (opacity safe) |\n| Page-level transitions | `page` → `600ms` | `ease-out` | Skip or instant |\n| Skeleton shimmer | `1400ms` | `ease-in-out` | Static color, no animation |\n| Focus ring appearance | `fast` → `100ms` | `ease-out` | No change |\n\n### 5.6 Z-Index Token Bindings\n\n| Layer | Token | Value |\n|---|---|---|\n| TopNavigationBar | `sticky` | `1100` |\n| Drawer backdrop | *(sticky − 1)* | `1099` |\n| NotificationsDrawer panel | `modal` | `1200` |\n\n### 5.7 Focus Ring Token Binding (Universal)\n\n```\noutline: 2px solid #0F6E56   /* border-focus / cta-primary */\noutline-offset: 2px\n```\nApplied to: all `<button>`, `<a>`, `<input>`, focusable `<div role=\"...\">` elements site-wide.\n\n---\n\n## 6. State Specifications\n\n### 6.1 Interactive State Matrix\n\n| State | Visual Treatment | Token |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Default** | Base surface + elevation level 1 | `surface-elevated` |\n| **Hover** | `+8%` opacity overlay on surface | `hover_opacity: 0.08`, `fast: 100ms` |\n| **Focus** | `2px solid deep-teal`, `2px offset` | `focus_ring` |\n| **Active/Pressed** | `+16%` opacity overlay | `subtle: 0.1` approx |\n| **Disabled** | `38%` opacity; `cursor: not-allowed` | `disabled_opacity: 0.38` |\n| **Loading** | Skeleton screen; `aria-busy=\"true\"` | `surface-elevated` shimmer |\n| **Error** | `coral-accent` border + icon + message | `border-error`, `error` |\n| **Empty** | Illustrated empty state + CTA | `surface-elevated` |\n\n### 6.2 Notification Drawer State\n\n| State | Behavior |\n|---|---|\n| **Closed** | Not rendered (or `display:none` / `aria-hidden=\"true\"`) |\n| **"
